import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Admin from './Admin'
import Ajout from './Ajout'

function Menu() {
    return (
       <BrowserRouter>
       <nav>

       </nav>

       <Route to="/admin123" component={Admin} exact/>
       <Redirect from="/admin123/reload" to="/admin123" />
       
       </BrowserRouter>
    )
}

export default Menu
